OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPubs seek relaxed alcohol  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flaws for World Cup final   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pubs are calling for licensing laws to 
OL,6, be relaxed to allow venues to serve    
OL,7, alcohol from 10:00 BST ahead of the    
OL,8, Women's World Cup final on Sunday.     
OL,10,FThe British Beer and Pub Association   
OL,11,F(BBPA) wants pubs to be able to sell   
OL,12,Fdrinks before kick-off.                
OL,14,FThe BBC understands it is unlikely as  
OL,15,FMPs would need to return to Westminster
OL,16,Fto change the rules temporarily.       
OL,18,FPubs can open when they choose on      
OL,19,FSundays, but when they can sell alcohol
OL,20,Fdepends on each pub's licence.         
